name: Two sides of the soul V2

metadata.name: ASH
metadata.description:
This is Lucy and Ash. The girl of the light and the girl of the fire. The portrait's name is Ash because her word is the most important in every situation. In the matter of difficult situations, Ash has the final word.
Lucy is more soft, thinking. She thinks a lot pending the decisions.
Ash always supports Lucy mentally. She makes Lucy more decisive and passionate.

At the end of the auction every bidder will receive the special stamp.

Technique: Procreate
Size: 4000x4000, 600dpi
